title: rambles from rhys - 11/23/18
body:
can I just say how much nostalgia watching VintageBeef’s youtube videos brings me? I remember that one year, I was having such a hard time and I needed comfort because school was hard, people were awful to me, and I felt alone, so I went on youtube to watch stuff. I found Dan and Phil’s channels and while they were great, they didn’t compare to VintageBeef. I’d come home from school and immediately sit down, curled up underneath a blanket, and watch one of his Minecraft videos, and once he started talking, it was like someone put a comfort blanket on top of me. This youtuber means so much to me and sometimes I get emotional, babey!!! so yeah VintageBeef is my favorite youtuber and will always have a special place in my heart.

also I’m gonna go play Minecraft now bye
